\begin_layout Lemma
A generalized 
\begin_inset Formula $k$
\end_inset

-Riemann invariant 
\begin_inset Formula $\phi$
\end_inset

 is constant along the trajectory of 
\begin_inset Formula $\ket{R_{k}}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Proof
\begin_inset Formula $\ip{\grad{\phi}}{R_{k}}$
\end_inset

