\begin_layout Proof
The constancy of 
\begin_inset Formula $\phi$
\end_inset

 along 
\begin_inset Formula $C_{k}$
\end_inset

 (the trajectory of 
\begin_inset Formula $\ket{R_{k}}$
\end_inset

) leads to an algebraic equation
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\phi\left(U_{1},\dots,U_{m}\right)=C
\]

\end_inset

